Hello Phillip and Ken-

I loved reading the JMLR paper. A few quick questions.

1) Did you try it without drawing the paths? How does that affect
performance?

2) Why did you use the function set you did? I notice it is different from
the typical set.

3) I see you trained on a task then transferred to an easier task (a larger
field)? Did you try the other way?

Congrats again. Very impressive results!


Best regards,
Jeff Clune
